moji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱 個女人柒得好緊要 仲要教返個細路轉頭 屌你老味俾我就同個細路講 <br />\n你大個千祈唔好學哥哥咁聽到嘟嘟聲都衝入嚟 你老母就係學左我 搞到漏低左架bb車喇</blockquote><br />\n呢句好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7dd301b7a705103c6450bdce7488b07b554f3c","tid":324472,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T12:59:00.000Z","msg":"無聽過話要行入車廂中間，企入啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一行入去就撳電話，好易俾人撞"},{"pid":"b4b4fea3fef97eb3a0af25a88c2996f33c7c1673","tid":324472,"uid":109957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T13:00:27.000Z","msg":"理性討論吓啫，大家唔好咁惡啦，想知係咪成日有類似的事，而你哋會點做，可能我入世未深，下次我會注意啦，對唔住各位"},{"pid":"fdd858b34a2dd90105b3445ce856f1fe7178b885","tid":324472,"uid":109957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T13:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>趣聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你自己聽到廣播衝入車廂<br />\n又覺得其他人唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但其實我有充裕時間，嗰時仲係廣播緊</blockquote><br />\n不如你背一次佢個廣播係咩先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n類似話[閘門即將關門&hellip;&hellip;]"},{"pid":"132f234cdd6276278545126af0100eb75cb3a8ae","tid":324472,"uid":3239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T13:01:58.000Z","msg":"推BB車仲衝, 抵死<br />\n衝得就預左要小心, 仲話返人轉頭<br />\n<br />\n不過嗌颯就多鳩餘, 佢都唔會認錯架啦, 盞谷鳩氣"},{"pid":"df292caa3ac4f41422fbe1aed01a9b4f941e5054","tid":324472,"uid":109957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T13:03:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>趣聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你自己聽到廣播衝入車廂<br />\n又覺得其他人唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解明知自己推住bb車都仲要衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱 個女人柒得好